Net Realized Gains/Losses
The Company had investment sales totaling $85.3 million and $496.7 million, respectively, for the three and nine months ended December 31, 2006 versus $102.6 million and $361.3 million, respectively, for the three and nine months ended December 31, 2005. Total net realized losses and gains, respectively for the three and nine months ended December 31, 2006 were $0.5 million and $26.3 million versus total net realized gains for the three and nine months ended December 31, 2005 of $4.7 million and $10.9 million. Included in the total net realized gains or losses are currency losses of $3.5 million and $7.0 million, respectively, for the three and nine months ended December 31, 2006 versus currency gains of $2.6 million and $5.4 million for the three and nine months ended December 31, 2005.
