Item 8.01 Other Events
On April 16, 2007, a press release was issued announcing that an affiliate of Apollo Investment Corporation (the "Purchaser") has entered into an Agreement and Plan of Merger (the "Agreement") with Innkeepers USA Trust, a Maryland real estate investment trust ("Innkeepers"), pursuant to which Innkeepers has agreed to be acquired by the Purchaser for $17.75 per share in cash, plus the assumption of Innkeepers indebtedness. A press release announcing the Agreement is attached hereto as Exhibit 99.1.
