On October 16, 2008 Apollo Investment Corporation (the "Company") announced that Ashok N. Bakhru has been appointed to the Board of Directors (the "Board") to serve as a member of the Board effective immediately. Mr. Bakhru will also serve as a member of the Nominating and Corporate Governance Committee and the Audit Committee of the Board. A copy of the press release announcing the appointment of Mr. Bakhru to the Board is attached hereto as Exhibit 99.1.
 
